data.description: Seller has received multiple offers and will make a decision by 5 Thursday at the latest . Completely renovated home !!! Newer roof and AC. Fresh paint inside and out. New flooring throughout. Fully renovated bathrooms and updated kitchen !! New stainless appliances including smooth cook top. Split floorplan. Newer white vinyl windows. Master has huge stand alone shower. Covered front porch and fenced in backyard.  Large screened in back porch perfect for entertaining ,private back yard. 3rd bedroom can be used for a bedroom or FLEX room ...right off living room to the left . Large inside laundry room. Painted inside and out !!
